qas.question: What types of cameras have proven to be much more sensitive to light than film?
What ISO equivalent speeds can digital cameras obtain?

answers.text: Faster processors, as well as advances in software noise reduction techniques

plausible_answers.text: advances in software noise reduction techniques

qas.question: What, besides a faster processor, prevents processing from happening when a photo is taken?

plausible_answers.text: images that have a higher level of refinement

qas.question: What could earlier generations of digital cameras store?
